  "name": {
    "en": "France CTC Flow 2 (B2B Clearance)",
    "fr": "France CTC Flux 2 (Clearance B2B)"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "Support for Flow 2 (\"facturation\") of the French CTC\nreform: domestic B2B clearance, applied to invoices\nexchanged between two parties identifiable as French\n(SIREN or French VAT ID on both sides). Built on the\nEU EN16931 CIUS profile (declared as a dependency).",
    "fr": "Support du Flux 2 (« facturation ») de la réforme\nfrançaise CTC : clearance B2B domestique appliquée aux\nfactures émises entre deux parties identifiables comme\nfrançaises (SIREN ou TVA française des deux côtés).\nBâti sur le profil CIUS EU EN16931 (déclaré comme\ndépendance)."
  },
  "sources": [
    {
      "title": {
        "en": "External Specifications",
        "fr": "Spécifications Externes"
      },
      "url": "https://www.impots.gouv.fr/specifications-externes-b2b"
    }
  ],
